== Hardware specs ==
All variants of this model come with 5th-gen Intel processors and have an option of a touchscreen with HD+ display.

* [http://ark.intel.com/products/84697/Intel-Core-i3-5010U-Processor-3M-Cache-2_10-GHz i3-5010U], [http://ark.intel.com/products/85212/Intel-Core-i5-5200U-Processor-3M-Cache-up-to-2_70-GHz i5-5200U], or [http://ark.intel.com/products/85214/Intel-Core-i7-5500U-Processor-4M-Cache-up-to-3_00-GHz i7-5500U] processor
* 13.3" LCD screen (3200x1800 touchscreen display or 1920x1080 without touchscreen)
* Broadwell-U Integrated Graphics
* 4-8 GB DDR3 1600MHz RAM
* 128-256 GB Samsung SSD
* 2x USB 3 ports
* mini-DisplayPort output
* Broadcom DW1560 802.11a/b/g/n/ac + Bluetooth 4.0

